  NOTE: Off-cliff form gives 0.16385, not 12/11.
  The formula must be evaluated AT the cliff (k = k_c).
  At k_c, the derivative diverges: the damping exponent INVERTS.
  (dC/dk)^(-1/5) -> (dC/dk)^(+1/5) at the cliff fixed point.

